{"tid":596315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1992年拆福州古蹟起豪宅　李嘉誠累習近平孭鑊","createTime":"2018-03-17T13:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T03:29:50.000Z","uid":5195,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4a504ca13b7be75197a34a8c3b5d9ce0309990","tid":596315,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180317/large/a0702a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180317%2Flarge%2Fa0702a.gif&h=16f2e3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】李嘉誠因何在習近平時代遭冷待，外界有諸多揣測，包括內地經濟強大不再在乎境外資本、特首選舉李撐唐英年而非中央意屬的梁振英得罪北京等。消息指，李早年投資福州「三坊七巷」失當累習揹黑鍋，或種禍根。<br />\n三坊七巷是福州老城區一組明清古建築群簡稱，被視為是福州的歷史之源、文化之根。1992年，時任中共福州市委書記習近平為改造這個舊區，市政府與長實簽約，計劃將三坊七巷改造成集文物和商貿、旅遊、文化、住宅、娛樂於一體的街區。李當時許諾對該項目投資30億元人民幣（下同，約37億港元），並親自到福州參加項目奠基儀式，晚宴上罕有地開懷暢飲孔府酒，還逐枱敬酒與官員打成一片，飲至面紅耳熱。市委書記習近平顯然十分重視李嘉誠的投資，陪同李在福州四處視察。<br />\n2005年被收地<br />\n一期工程「衣錦華庭」完成後，效果令外界啞然；原三坊七巷衣錦坊大片老宅被拆除，古街區被削掉一角，光祿坊和吉庇巷被闢為馬路，古蹟變華庭住宅，舊貌蕩然無存，輿論譁然，質疑李嘉誠名為改造古蹟，實為借古蹟賺錢。<br />\n2005年，福州當局中止與長實的50年合同，收回土地使用權，其時習近平早已調離福建到浙江任職。但輿論矛頭仍指向習，認為習對事件負有一定責任，成為政壇對手攻擊習的把柄。2006年，福州市籌措30多億元對三坊七巷修復保護。"},{"pid":"7dfb7d99ff4c429099dbf7b3779b16b4882f629f","tid":596315,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"方丈份人。。。"},{"pid":"37fc6e42c8be222e0adf2af22905f31aa9ce0857","tid":596315,"uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"7dfb7d99ff4c429099dbf7b3779b16b4882f629f","tid":596315,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"方丈份人。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20141101/large/1414825106_5a73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20141101%2Flarge%2F1414825106_5a73.jpg&h=4feaafd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"257a421cab9d8b46e269b3fef0e4a222807b495f","tid":596315,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc558c09e5b8e0279b0d2fde4596ef86ddb4522e","tid":596315,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>方丈份人。。。</blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20141101/large/1414825106_5a73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20141101%2Flarge%2F1414825106_5a73.jpg&h=4feaafd9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n張學友？"},{"pid":"6438c399a78ff6670cf893d7c5f1a6c584e04212","tid":596315,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/220023_a48dfba04ed6fecd83ea9e5556bce487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F220023_a48dfba04ed6fecd83ea9e5556bce487.jpg&h=bb29c8e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0007fca9471c689d2c24b1dfcd89628433c0a34","tid":596315,"uid":34103,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd204309d3cc883c828d16c69bf70844590e5183","tid":596315,"uid":85659,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得走佬走咁急"},{"pid":"d8b2dae180e86c69d70108bc1a3be7a04a2cccba","tid":596315,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1620fff683b61060ffba02bdc742e8907fb2dfc","tid":596315,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"1949年以後，吉庇巷（今名吉庇路）、楊橋巷（今名楊橋路）和光祿坊改建為馬路，所以現在保存的實際只有二坊五巷。<br />\n<br />\n2006年12月，水榭戲台修復工程正式動工，標誌著三坊七巷文保單位修復工程全面展開。2007年福州市政府頒布了《福州市三坊七巷歷史文化街區古建築搬遷修復保護辦法》。整個工程總投資達40億元，全面修復159座明清古建築，2010年基本完成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3e/Map_of_Three_Lanes_and_Seven_Alleys.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3e%2FMap_of_Three_Lanes_and_Seven_Alleys.gif&h=359cac7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ccb8f7ac21c3e64b736b563a7e037eef2bd7950","tid":596315,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image4.cityhouse.cn/fuzhou/images/prop/large/35/d5/201801271411255147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage4.cityhouse.cn%2Ffuzhou%2Fimages%2Fprop%2Flarge%2F35%2Fd5%2F201801271411255147.jpg&h=dedd18ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正丫, 呢d view 一定唔會起幢樓遮住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d48c124ac1dbb6d360a3b89525a7cc31a72681","tid":596315,"uid":132587,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"好佩服李嘉誠咁陰質 都咁多香港人當佢神咁拜<br />\n包括呢度"},{"pid":"450d262de6e3a317ee70b1172c2e90facef657b8","tid":596315,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ad1307077399032f59f1783e8d54d979955d62","tid":596315,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d4d48c124ac1dbb6d360a3b89525a7cc31a72681","tid":596315,"uid":132587,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"好佩服李嘉誠咁陰質 都咁多香港人當佢神咁拜<br />\n包括呢度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"有錢始終上等人"},{"pid":"e545e6d96d6f4a7c363b4dc1e3ede80168f5ac8d","tid":596315,"uid":35